ref> To the south it borders communes of [[V\u1ea1n Ninh, Qu\u1ea3ng B\u00ecnh|V\u1ea1n Ninh]] and [[An Ninh, Qu\u1ea3ng B\u00ecnh|An Ninh]], to the southeast it borders [[H\u1ed3ng Th\u1ee7y, L\u1ec7 Th\u1ee7y|H\u1ed3ng Th\u1ee7y]] in district of [[L\u1ec7 Th\u1ee7y]], to the east is communes of [[Gia Ninh]], to the north is commune of [[Duy Ninh]], to the west is commune of [[Hi\u1ec1n Ninh, Qu\u1ea3ng B\u00ecnh|Hi\u1ec1n Ninh]]. The communes contains six villages: [[Qu\u1ea3ng X\u00e1]], [[H\u00f2a B\u00ecnh, Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh|H\u00f2a B\u00ecnh]], [[Nguy\u1ec7t \u00c1ng]], [[Th\u1ebf L\u1ed9c]], [[H\u1eefu T\u00e2n]], and [[T\u00e2n Th\u00e0nh, T\u00e2n Ninh|T\u00e2n Th\u00e0nh]].\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n{{Quang Binh Province}}\n\n{{coord|10|20|N|106|27|E|display=title|region:VN_type:city_source:GNS-enwiki}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Tan Ninh}}\n[[Category:Populated places in Qu\u1ea3ng B\u00ecnh Province]]\n[[Category:Communes of Qu\u1ea3ng B\u00ecnh Province]]\n{{QuangBinh-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Settlement\n<!--See the Table at Infobox Settlement for all fields and descriptions of usage-->\n<!-- Basic info  ---------------->\n|name          = T\u00e2n Ninh\n|other_name             =\n|native_name            =  <!-- for cities whose native name is not in English -->\n|nickname               = \n|settlement_type        =[[Commune-level subdivisions (Vietnam)|Commune]] and village\n|motto                  =\n<!-- images and maps  ----------->\n|image_skyline          = \n|imagesize              = \n|image_caption          = \n|image_flag             = \n|flag_size              =\n|image_seal             = \n|seal_size              =\n|image_shield           = \n|shield_size            =\n|image_map              = \n|mapsize                = \n|map_caption            = \n|pushpin_map            =<!-- the name of a location map as per http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Template:Location_map -->\n|pushpin_label_position =top\n|pushpin_mapsize        =300\n|pus